Description: Ball Square area, 3.5 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment. A brisk, 13-minute walk to Davis. Has free in-building laundry as well as 1 off-street parking space. Notable amenities include a dining room, hardwood floors, a living room, a modern bath, a porch and a yard. The eat-in kitchen features a gas range and microwave. Broker fee may apply.
